From one-legged to fake mud and nearly-naked, month-by-month jeans are getting weirder and weirder. And now detachable jeans have arrived thanks to Y/Project. The beyond unusual Detachable Cut-Out Front Jeans retail for a solid £325. There are butt slits at the back and painful-looking shorts involved. And, boy, do we have questions...           (H/T: Metro)